1
00:00:01,001 --> 00:00:03,712
[SOFTLY] <i>Macky broke the bomb transmitter.</i>

2
00:00:03,795 --> 00:00:06,548
<i>It's been deactivated.</i>
<i>It won't explode anymore.</i>

3
00:00:06,631 --> 00:00:08,216
<i>Macky has a plan.</i>

4
00:00:08,299 --> 00:00:09,384
<i>I also have a plan.</i>

5
00:00:09,467 --> 00:00:11,219
<i>My mother told me</i>

6
00:00:11,302 --> 00:00:13,596
<i>my real father is still alive, and…</i>

7
00:00:13,680 --> 00:00:15,682
<i>I really feel that it's you.</i>

8
00:00:15,765 --> 00:00:18,518
[HOMER] <i>If you're really my son,</i>
<i>what do you want to happen?</i>

9
00:00:18,601 --> 00:00:19,936
[OLSEN] <i>Let Mama go.</i>

10
00:00:20,020 --> 00:00:21,521
<i>Why don't we start over?</i>

11
00:00:22,939 --> 00:00:25,483
[MACKY] <i>I can't stand this anymore!</i>
<i>I've had enough!</i>

12
00:00:25,567 --> 00:00:26,943
<i>Are you out of your mind?!</i>

13
00:00:27,027 --> 00:00:29,779
- [FIN] <i>Fine! Go! I won't stop you!</i>
- [MACKY]<i> I'm really leaving.</i>

14
00:00:29,863 --> 00:00:31,865
<i>All you do is cause trouble anyway!</i>

15
00:00:31,948 --> 00:00:34,409
- [BLOW LANDS]
- [LUCAS] <i>Hey!</i>

16
00:00:34,492 --> 00:00:36,327
- [LUCAS] <i>You really won't stop?!</i>
- [ICE] <i>Don't hurt him!</i>

17
00:00:36,411 --> 00:00:37,537
[BLOW LANDS]

18
00:00:37,620 --> 00:00:40,331
- [EMIL] <i>Dado, come in.</i>
- [LIAM]<i> It's Emil Padua.</i>

19
00:00:40,415 --> 00:00:42,792
<i>We need to secure Dado</i>
<i>before Emil finds out.</i>

20
00:00:42,876 --> 00:00:44,544
<i>He might have told Emil!</i>

21
00:00:44,627 --> 00:00:47,255
<i>They might kill more hostages</i>
<i>if you attack them.</i>

22
00:00:47,338 --> 00:00:48,631
[AREZA] <i>All units, hold position!</i>

23
00:00:48,715 --> 00:00:50,341
[LIAM] <i>I have to go back upstairs.</i>

24
00:00:50,425 --> 00:00:52,093
<i>I can't let you attack them like this.</i>

25
00:00:52,177 --> 00:00:53,845
<i>If something happens to them,</i>
<i>it'll be my fault!</i>

26
00:00:53,928 --> 00:00:55,472
<i>We will negotiate with them.</i>

27
00:00:55,555 --> 00:00:57,682
<i>We can't negotiate with demons!</i>

28
00:00:57,766 --> 00:00:59,309
<i>They might've already gotten the money,</i>

29
00:00:59,392 --> 00:01:02,020
<i>but they don't know</i>
<i>how they'll get out of here.</i>

30
00:01:02,103 --> 00:01:04,147
<i>And we'll use that to negotiate.</i>

31
00:01:04,230 --> 00:01:08,109
<i>Lieutenant Areza was the one</i>
<i>who had evidence gathered against you.</i>

32
00:01:08,193 --> 00:01:09,944
<i>You have a connection with Emil Padua.</i>

33
00:01:10,028 --> 00:01:12,030
<i>I am not the mastermind</i>

34
00:01:12,113 --> 00:01:14,699
<i>of the hostage taking at La Playa Roja.</i>

35
00:01:14,783 --> 00:01:16,534
<i>It's not Emil Padua.</i>

36
00:01:16,618 --> 00:01:20,622
<i>Greta Roja is the real mastermind</i>

37
00:01:20,705 --> 00:01:22,957
<i>of the hostage taking at La Playa Roja.</i>

38
00:01:23,625 --> 00:01:24,709
<i>Liam escaped.</i>

39
00:01:24,793 --> 00:01:26,961
[EMIL] <i>We'll teach Liam Roja a lesson.</i>

40
00:01:27,045 --> 00:01:29,005
<i>We'll kill his mother.</i>

41
00:01:32,634 --> 00:01:36,679
[PENSIVE MUSIC PLAYING]

42
00:01:38,306 --> 00:01:39,349
[LUNA] Doc.

43
00:01:40,850 --> 00:01:42,602
I need to go after Liam.

44
00:01:43,853 --> 00:01:45,730
I have a bad feeling about this.

45
00:01:47,190 --> 00:01:48,650
I hope I'm wrong.

46
00:01:49,234 --> 00:01:50,360
Luna,

47
00:01:50,443 --> 00:01:52,570
Liam just saved your life.

48
00:01:52,654 --> 00:01:54,614
Now you're going
to put yourself in danger again?

49
00:01:55,532 --> 00:01:56,908
And what can you do?

50
00:01:56,991 --> 00:02:01,955
Doc, you weren't at the resort
when those demons came.

51
00:02:02,038 --> 00:02:04,791
If you'd seen then
how Liam and I fought them,

52
00:02:04,874 --> 00:02:06,292
you wouldn't worry so much.

53
00:02:08,336 --> 00:02:10,713
See! There it is again.

54
00:02:12,090 --> 00:02:14,843
You think my friendship with Liam
is more than that.

55
00:02:15,468 --> 00:02:17,679
No, I believe you now.

56
00:02:17,762 --> 00:02:19,639
You guys are really just friends.

57
00:02:20,723 --> 00:02:25,520
It's because of the things you said
when you were under anesthesia.

58
00:02:27,730 --> 00:02:29,023
[WHISTLES FAINTLY]

59
00:02:29,107 --> 00:02:32,610
[PLAYFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

60
00:02:32,694 --> 00:02:34,737
[MOCKINGLY] "He's just like you, Doc.

61
00:02:34,821 --> 00:02:36,990
Very handsome."

62
00:02:38,366 --> 00:02:39,993
"Do you have a girlfriend?"

63
00:02:41,744 --> 00:02:43,413
"I'm single, by the way."

64
00:02:44,622 --> 00:02:46,124
"Liam and I aren't together."

65
00:02:47,208 --> 00:02:48,710
"But…

66
00:02:48,793 --> 00:02:50,420
we can be together."

67
00:02:53,006 --> 00:02:54,632
[SLAPS SOFTLY]

68
00:02:54,716 --> 00:02:56,593
I didn't say that.

69
00:02:56,676 --> 00:02:58,469
You're making things up.

70
00:03:00,805 --> 00:03:02,765
No, I'm just trying to make you laugh.

71
00:03:03,766 --> 00:03:04,851
Whatever.

72
00:03:05,768 --> 00:03:08,771
Hey, don't worry about Liam.

73
00:03:08,855 --> 00:03:10,481
He's with a cop now.

74
00:03:10,565 --> 00:03:12,567
Doc, I'm okay.

75
00:03:12,650 --> 00:03:13,860
Come on, please.

76
00:03:13,943 --> 00:03:15,361
Let me do this.

77
00:03:15,445 --> 00:03:16,779
Doc Ivan.

78
00:03:18,323 --> 00:03:20,366
- Doc.
- Yes?

79
00:03:20,450 --> 00:03:24,287
Do you know anyone
we can catch a ride home with?

80
00:03:24,370 --> 00:03:27,498
She's right. We really want
to get out of here.

81
00:03:27,582 --> 00:03:29,667
Doc, please. We don't want
to be here anymore.

82
00:03:29,751 --> 00:03:31,711
We're so stressed out.

83
00:03:31,794 --> 00:03:33,588
- [SHUTTER CLICKS]
- [IVAN] All right.

84
00:03:33,671 --> 00:03:36,382
- There's a car that can take you home.
- Thank you.

85
00:03:37,383 --> 00:03:38,509
Luna?

86
00:03:39,052 --> 00:03:45,016
[OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING]

87
00:03:49,395 --> 00:03:55,485
[OMINOUS MUSIC SWELLS]

88
00:03:58,947 --> 00:04:00,365
[MUSIC FADES]

89
00:04:00,448 --> 00:04:02,325
[PHONE RINGING]

90
00:04:03,368 --> 00:04:05,036
- Hello?
- [GLUM MUSIC PLAYING]

91
00:04:05,119 --> 00:04:07,997
[MILA] I've been calling you!

92
00:04:09,499 --> 00:04:11,793
[LUCAS]<i> I'm sorry.</i>
<i>Things got a bit chaotic earlier.</i>

93
00:04:12,669 --> 00:04:13,711
<i>What's the problem?</i>

94
00:04:14,295 --> 00:04:15,129
[MILA] <i>Lucas.</i>

95
00:04:15,838 --> 00:04:18,341
Tell Boss Emil that you have
to leave the building now.

96
00:04:18,424 --> 00:04:20,468
[GLUM MUSIC CONTINUES]

97
00:04:21,052 --> 00:04:28,017
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

98
00:04:42,490 --> 00:04:43,449
[MILA] Right now!

99
00:04:43,533 --> 00:04:49,664
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

100
00:04:51,249 --> 00:04:52,083
[MILA GASPS]

101
00:04:52,166 --> 00:04:54,752
- Mila? Mila?
- [LINE DISCONNECTS]

102
00:05:03,219 --> 00:05:09,100
[THEME MUSIC PLAYING]

103
00:05:39,088 --> 00:05:42,133
- Lucas? Boss Emil?
- No--

104
00:05:42,216 --> 00:05:44,969
- Were you talking to Lucas Sebastian?
- [BREATHING SHAKILY]

105
00:05:45,053 --> 00:05:46,471
Answer my question.

106
00:05:47,305 --> 00:05:49,057
It's none of your business.

107
00:05:54,270 --> 00:05:55,313
What is it?

108
00:05:56,189 --> 00:05:57,815
- That was Mila.
- [PENSIVE MUSIC PLAYING]

109
00:05:57,899 --> 00:06:01,027
She said we need to get out of here now.

110
00:06:01,110 --> 00:06:01,986
Why?

111
00:06:02,070 --> 00:06:03,613
She didn't say.

112
00:06:04,739 --> 00:06:06,532
Maybe your wife is just getting anxious.

113
00:06:06,616 --> 00:06:09,410
[PENSIVE MUSIC CONTINUES]

114
00:06:10,953 --> 00:06:13,081
You're with the hostage takers.

115
00:06:13,164 --> 00:06:14,832
Admit it!

116
00:06:14,916 --> 00:06:18,503
- [MILA GRUNTS SHAKILY]
- [TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

117
00:06:18,586 --> 00:06:20,004
- [BLOW LANDS]
- [GROANS]

118
00:06:24,467 --> 00:06:25,843
Luna! Police!

119
00:06:25,927 --> 00:06:27,011
- [LUNA] Police!
- Police!

120
00:06:27,553 --> 00:06:29,972
- [LUNA] Doc! Police!
- [IVAN] She's with the hostage takers!

121
00:06:30,056 --> 00:06:32,517
- No! Let me go!
- Stop her!

122
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:34,185
Let me go!

123
00:06:34,268 --> 00:06:35,978
Let me go!

124
00:06:36,062 --> 00:06:37,021
Calm down, ma'am.

125
00:06:37,105 --> 00:06:38,231
Let me go! [SOBBING]

126
00:06:38,314 --> 00:06:41,567
[MILA BREATHING HEAVILY]

127
00:06:45,613 --> 00:06:46,614
[GRUNTS]

128
00:06:46,697 --> 00:06:49,575
Please! Please, please, please!

129
00:06:51,077 --> 00:06:57,250
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

130
00:07:11,264 --> 00:07:17,520
[TENSE MUSIC SWELLS]

131
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:24,068
[GUN COCKS]

132
00:07:24,152 --> 00:07:29,866
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

133
00:07:42,795 --> 00:07:44,422
What's wrong, Boss Emil?

134
00:07:47,758 --> 00:07:54,265
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

135
00:08:09,822 --> 00:08:12,658
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

136
00:08:12,742 --> 00:08:14,619
Do we still have time?

137
00:08:20,374 --> 00:08:23,586
Any mistake could put
the hostages at risk.

138
00:08:23,669 --> 00:08:25,421
We won't make a mistake.

139
00:08:25,505 --> 00:08:27,798
And when they take the bait?

140
00:08:27,882 --> 00:08:29,383
Then we'll move.

141
00:08:30,092 --> 00:08:31,636
We'll go inside.

142
00:08:31,719 --> 00:08:34,013
We'll go straight for their leader.

143
00:08:34,096 --> 00:08:40,144
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

144
00:08:46,609 --> 00:08:50,404
[SINISTER MUSIC PLAYING]

145
00:08:50,488 --> 00:08:52,323
What are you going to do to me?!

146
00:08:53,950 --> 00:08:57,578
[SINISTER MUSIC SWELLS]

147
00:08:57,662 --> 00:09:01,374
I will make your son pay
for what he did to me.

148
00:09:03,042 --> 00:09:08,130
[SINISTER MUSIC CONTINUES]

149
00:09:08,214 --> 00:09:11,008
[LIAM] <i>Emil Padua, this is Liam Roja.</i>

150
00:09:12,093 --> 00:09:13,553
<i>- Let's talk.</i>
- [RADIO STATIC]

151
00:09:15,012 --> 00:09:18,474
Speaking of the devil.

152
00:09:20,226 --> 00:09:21,686
What do you want to happen?

153
00:09:21,769 --> 00:09:23,229
[LIAM] <i>I've spoken to the police.</i>

154
00:09:24,438 --> 00:09:27,066
If you can make sure
that the hostages are safe,

155
00:09:27,775 --> 00:09:30,027
you will be able to get out safely.

156
00:09:30,111 --> 00:09:34,740
You still don't know me, boy.

157
00:09:35,408 --> 00:09:37,660
[EMIL] <i>My rules are simple.</i>

158
00:09:38,244 --> 00:09:40,580
If someone makes a mistake
or commits a sin…

159
00:09:40,663 --> 00:09:45,084
[DARK MUSIC PLAYING]

160
00:09:45,167 --> 00:09:46,752
…they will be punished.

161
00:09:46,836 --> 00:09:49,964
[DARK MUSIC CONTINUES]

162
00:09:50,047 --> 00:09:52,008
Now since you wronged me,

163
00:09:52,842 --> 00:09:56,470
I will punish your mother.

164
00:09:57,096 --> 00:09:58,180
I am begging you.

165
00:09:58,264 --> 00:10:00,933
I am begging you, Emil.
Please, don't. Please!

166
00:10:02,101 --> 00:10:03,060
[GRETA WHIMPERS]

167
00:10:03,144 --> 00:10:04,395
Ma?

168
00:10:04,478 --> 00:10:09,734
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

169
00:10:09,817 --> 00:10:11,277
- [GUNSHOT]
- Ma!

170
00:10:11,944 --> 00:10:13,029
- [EMIL GROANS]
- [LUCAS] Boss!

171
00:10:13,112 --> 00:10:13,988
[GUN COCKS]

172
00:10:14,071 --> 00:10:14,989
Nobody move!

173
00:10:17,241 --> 00:10:19,702
I repeat, we need backup on the rooftop.

174
00:10:19,785 --> 00:10:20,911
Let's move!

175
00:10:20,995 --> 00:10:27,168
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

176
00:10:27,251 --> 00:10:28,628
[GROANS]

177
00:10:29,378 --> 00:10:31,297
- Stay down!
- [BLOWS LAND]

178
00:10:32,590 --> 00:10:35,051
- Go on! Get out of here!
- [MACKY GRUNTS]

179
00:10:35,718 --> 00:10:42,683
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

180
00:10:45,102 --> 00:10:46,854
You can't escape!

181
00:10:46,937 --> 00:10:48,189
We'll blow you up!

182
00:10:49,857 --> 00:10:50,941
Get out of here!

183
00:10:51,984 --> 00:10:53,069
[MACKY GRUNTS]

184
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:56,197
[MACKY] Nice try.

185
00:10:56,280 --> 00:10:57,948
[SENATOR MARISTELLA] Let's go!

186
00:10:58,449 --> 00:10:59,617
- Hurry!
- Come on!

187
00:10:59,700 --> 00:11:01,243
Be careful, Homer!

188
00:11:01,327 --> 00:11:02,620
[MACKY] Come on!

189
00:11:02,703 --> 00:11:04,372
Put it down, Homer!

190
00:11:04,455 --> 00:11:05,998
- Go on!
- [GRUNTS]

191
00:11:06,916 --> 00:11:08,000
[GUN COCKS]

192
00:11:09,043 --> 00:11:15,466
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

193
00:11:21,222 --> 00:11:22,932
Give me your gun, Homer!

194
00:11:24,767 --> 00:11:26,102
Give it!

195
00:11:26,852 --> 00:11:27,812
Come on!

196
00:11:28,396 --> 00:11:29,647
I'll kill him!

197
00:11:30,231 --> 00:11:32,650
Well, Pa?!

198
00:11:34,318 --> 00:11:35,319
Come on!

199
00:11:36,028 --> 00:11:37,196
All right, good.

200
00:11:37,279 --> 00:11:44,286
[MUSIC TURNS TENSE]

201
00:11:54,630 --> 00:12:00,010
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

202
00:12:16,610 --> 00:12:23,576
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

203
00:12:30,791 --> 00:12:33,586
[GUNSHOTS]

204
00:12:34,962 --> 00:12:35,838
[GUNSHOTS]

205
00:12:35,921 --> 00:12:36,797
[SHOUTS]

206
00:12:37,506 --> 00:12:40,926
[RAPID GUNFIRE]

207
00:12:45,764 --> 00:12:47,183
[GUNSHOTS]

208
00:12:49,226 --> 00:12:50,644
Move! Move!

209
00:12:51,604 --> 00:12:53,689
[GUNSHOTS]

210
00:12:54,482 --> 00:12:57,902
[GUNSHOTS]

211
00:12:59,612 --> 00:13:02,907
[GUNSHOTS]

212
00:13:02,990 --> 00:13:04,992
[RAPID GUNFIRE]

213
00:13:07,661 --> 00:13:10,831
Homer, don't let your son get away!

214
00:13:10,915 --> 00:13:11,957
Yes, boss.

215
00:13:17,588 --> 00:13:18,631
[DADO] Fredo, stand up!

216
00:13:21,175 --> 00:13:22,760
[GUN CLICKS]

217
00:13:22,843 --> 00:13:24,053
Fredo!

218
00:13:25,471 --> 00:13:26,430
[GRUNTS]

219
00:13:29,099 --> 00:13:32,144
[RAPID GUNFIRE]

220
00:13:32,728 --> 00:13:33,854
[SENATOR MARISTELLA] Let's go!

221
00:13:34,897 --> 00:13:36,524
Hurry! Go!

222
00:13:36,607 --> 00:13:38,526
- Son, come on!
- [MACKY] Dad!

223
00:13:38,609 --> 00:13:40,819
[PANTING]

224
00:13:40,903 --> 00:13:42,488
Keep running!

225
00:13:42,571 --> 00:13:43,614
[GRETA SCREAMS]

226
00:13:43,697 --> 00:13:45,407
Hurry! Hurry! Hurry!

227
00:13:46,992 --> 00:13:50,412
- They're catching up!
- Move! Move!

228
00:13:50,496 --> 00:13:54,208
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

229
00:13:54,291 --> 00:13:55,918
Keep running!

230
00:13:56,001 --> 00:13:57,711
Oh my God!

231
00:14:01,340 --> 00:14:02,424
Move, move.

232
00:14:02,508 --> 00:14:03,592
Go, go, go!

233
00:14:03,676 --> 00:14:08,013
[OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING]

234
00:14:09,139 --> 00:14:10,975
Boss, how are you?

235
00:14:11,767 --> 00:14:13,352
I can handle this.

236
00:14:13,435 --> 00:14:14,812
Go after Magnus!

237
00:14:14,895 --> 00:14:16,355
I need him alive.

238
00:14:17,189 --> 00:14:18,649
Yes, sir.

239
00:14:20,776 --> 00:14:25,197
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

240
00:14:30,369 --> 00:14:31,829
[RAPID GUNFIRE]

241
00:14:40,337 --> 00:14:46,635
[OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING]

242
00:14:47,845 --> 00:14:49,471
Papa!

243
00:14:52,516 --> 00:14:54,560
- [DADO] Hey!
- [SENATOR MARISTELLA] Hurry up, Macky!

244
00:14:54,643 --> 00:14:59,773
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

245
00:15:01,233 --> 00:15:03,027
[RAPID GUNFIRE]

246
00:15:04,153 --> 00:15:09,450
[RAPID GUNFIRE]

247
00:15:13,662 --> 00:15:18,584
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

248
00:15:30,095 --> 00:15:31,513
[GRUNTS]

249
00:15:33,599 --> 00:15:35,142
Gwen! Gwen!

250
00:15:35,935 --> 00:15:37,436
<i>Boss, what's happening?</i>

251
00:15:37,937 --> 00:15:41,106
Take Leni to the basement now!

252
00:15:41,815 --> 00:15:46,320
[OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING]

253
00:15:51,450 --> 00:15:53,285
- Let's go.
- Where are we going?

254
00:15:53,369 --> 00:15:54,495
Basement.

255
00:15:56,288 --> 00:15:57,456
[GRUNTS]

256
00:15:58,624 --> 00:16:00,167
- Ow!
- Come on.

257
00:16:00,250 --> 00:16:06,006
[OMINOUS MUSIC CONTINUES]

258
00:16:06,799 --> 00:16:12,221
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

259
00:16:15,641 --> 00:16:17,393
Let's go.

260
00:16:19,728 --> 00:16:21,188
Where are we going?

261
00:16:21,271 --> 00:16:22,564
Stop asking questions.

262
00:16:25,943 --> 00:16:31,865
[OMINOUS MUSIC CONTINUES]

263
00:16:33,450 --> 00:16:34,660
[SENATOR MARISTELLA] Go ahead!

264
00:16:34,743 --> 00:16:37,329
- [MACKY] Papa!
- They're catching up.

265
00:16:37,871 --> 00:16:39,581
Keep running!

266
00:16:42,376 --> 00:16:48,382
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

267
00:16:54,805 --> 00:16:56,390
[SENATOR MARISTELLA] Move, just run!

268
00:16:56,473 --> 00:16:58,392
Dad, what about you?

269
00:16:58,475 --> 00:16:59,643
Leave me!

270
00:16:59,727 --> 00:17:00,978
Hurry, move!

271
00:17:01,061 --> 00:17:02,062
Let's go!

272
00:17:05,607 --> 00:17:06,775
- Liam!
- Ma!

273
00:17:06,859 --> 00:17:08,068
Liam, son!

274
00:17:08,152 --> 00:17:09,987
I thought something had happened to you.

275
00:17:10,070 --> 00:17:12,823
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

276
00:17:14,450 --> 00:17:15,784
How?

277
00:17:16,660 --> 00:17:19,496
I need access to my email.

278
00:17:30,883 --> 00:17:37,681
[DARK MUSIC PLAYING]

279
00:17:37,765 --> 00:17:38,974
There.

280
00:17:39,558 --> 00:17:42,227
Everything you need to know is in there.

281
00:17:50,402 --> 00:17:51,570
[GRETA] <i>Captain Jacinto.</i>

282
00:17:51,653 --> 00:17:57,993
[DARK MUSIC CONTINUES]

283
00:18:02,998 --> 00:18:04,500
<i>Ten million.</i>

284
00:18:05,626 --> 00:18:07,461
<i>That's all I can give.</i>

285
00:18:08,879 --> 00:18:10,130
<i>I repeat,</i>

286
00:18:10,214 --> 00:18:13,258
<i>the job has to be clean</i>
<i>and no one gets hurt.</i>

287
00:18:13,342 --> 00:18:14,676
[CHUCKLES]

288
00:18:15,385 --> 00:18:17,179
<i>You're easy to talk to, Greta.</i>

289
00:18:18,013 --> 00:18:19,681
<i>Don't worry.</i>

290
00:18:19,765 --> 00:18:24,561
<i>As soon as the hostage taking is over,</i>
<i>I'll give you your share.</i>

291
00:18:25,145 --> 00:18:26,522
<i>Ten times the investment.</i>

292
00:18:27,189 --> 00:18:33,529
[DARK MUSIC CONTINUES]

293
00:18:40,619 --> 00:18:41,995
<i>The bomb didn't explode?</i>

294
00:18:42,079 --> 00:18:43,914
<i>Macky found the transmitter.</i>

295
00:18:43,997 --> 00:18:46,375
<i>He destroyed it so the bombs</i>
<i>wouldn't explode anymore.</i>

296
00:18:46,458 --> 00:18:49,128
<i>- Where's Papa?</i>
<i>- On the rooftop.</i>

297
00:18:49,211 --> 00:18:50,504
<i>With Olsen!</i>

298
00:18:50,587 --> 00:18:52,422
- [GUNSHOTS]
- [GROANS]

299
00:18:52,506 --> 00:18:54,633
[MACKY] <i>Dad!</i>

300
00:18:54,716 --> 00:18:56,677
<i>- Dad!</i>
- [SENATOR MARISTELLA GROANS]

301
00:18:56,760 --> 00:18:59,054
<i>Please, help Macky!</i>

302
00:18:59,138 --> 00:19:01,014
<i>Men, evacuate the hostages.</i>

303
00:19:01,098 --> 00:19:02,516
<i>- Let's move!</i>
- [OFFICER] <i>Move! Move!</i>

304
00:19:02,599 --> 00:19:04,935
<i>- Let's get out of here.</i>
<i>- Let's go!</i>

305
00:19:08,397 --> 00:19:09,231
<i>Freeze!</i>

306
00:19:11,024 --> 00:19:12,151
<i>Dad!</i>

307
00:19:22,077 --> 00:19:23,287
[SHOUTS]

308
00:19:24,163 --> 00:19:27,332
[BOTH GRUNTING]

309
00:19:31,628 --> 00:19:33,672
[LUCAS] <i>Come on!</i>
<i>Come at me!</i>

310
00:19:35,340 --> 00:19:37,551
<i>There are still hostages</i>
<i>that we haven't found.</i>

311
00:19:37,634 --> 00:19:39,511
<i>The Del Rosario family.</i>

312
00:19:39,595 --> 00:19:42,014
<i>Alert all men.</i>
<i>We need to arrest Greta Roja.</i>

313
00:19:42,097 --> 00:19:44,391
- [LIAM] <i>Let's go. Come on.</i>
<i>- Ma'am, come with us.</i>

314
00:19:44,474 --> 00:19:47,561
[GRETA] <i>Huh? No!</i>
<i>I'm not leaving!</i>

315
00:19:50,981 --> 00:19:53,775
- [EMIL GROANS]
- [DADO GRUNTS]

316
00:19:53,859 --> 00:19:55,402
<i>- Let's go!</i>
<i>- Can you walk, boss?</i>

317
00:19:55,485 --> 00:19:58,113
<i>I can do it! Come on!</i>

318
00:19:58,197 --> 00:19:59,698
- [DADO] <i>Fredo, let's go!</i>
- [EMIL GROANS]

319
00:20:00,490 --> 00:20:01,700
[CABRAL] <i>She can't escape.</i>

320
00:20:03,911 --> 00:20:06,538
[AREZA] <i>Some hostage takers may</i>
<i>still be here in the building.</i>

321
00:20:08,248 --> 00:20:11,084
[AREZA] <i>I have people guarding</i>
<i>the entrances and exits</i>

322
00:20:11,168 --> 00:20:13,212
<i>so they can't escape.</i>

323
00:20:13,295 --> 00:20:14,671
[EMIL GRUNTING]

324
00:20:16,131 --> 00:20:17,674
- [GRUNTS]
<i>- Hang in there, boss.</i>

325
00:20:17,758 --> 00:20:20,260
[GROANING]

326
00:20:20,928 --> 00:20:26,433
[THEME MUSIC PLAYING]
